            <lb n="N003"></lb><g ref="#para"></g> Wey<g ref="#combuml"></g>n von criechen wer die auz drucht <g ref="#para"></g><seg type="transpose" xml:id="_269r03"> gewiz</seg> <g ref="#tridotright"></g><note xml:lang="de">Gehört ans Ende von Zeile 2.</note><note xml:lang="en">Last word of line 2.</note>
				<lb n="N004"></lb>e daz <g ref="#slong">s</g>y envallent vnd czeitig werdent . da wirt ay<g ref="#combuml"></g>n trank avz daz
				<lb n="N005"></lb><g ref="#inodot">i</g><g ref="#slong">s</g>t gut fu<g ref="#combuml"></g>r dy ru<g ref="#combuml"></g>rr . von <abbr>chriech<ex>e</ex><am><g ref="#bar_e"></g></am>n</abbr> macht man auch lectwari <abbr><ex>etc.</ex><am><g ref="#etcamp"></g></am></abbr></seg><seg>
				<lb n="N006"></lb><g ref="#para"></g> Wer guten Roten wey<g ref="#combuml"></g>n haben wil . der <g ref="#slong">s</g>chol
