				<lb n="N010"></lb>dy<g ref="#combuml"></g> nicht czv clay<g ref="#combuml"></g>n <g ref="#slong">s</g>ei von <abbr>ay<g ref="#combuml"></g>ne<ex>m</ex><am><g ref="#bar_m"></g></am></abbr> holer dar in vnd <g ref="#slong">s</g>ecz ey<g ref="#combuml"></g>n <g ref="#slong">s</g>chu<g ref="#slong">s</g><g ref="#slong">s</g>el
				<lb n="N011"></lb>do<g ref="#rrot">r</g> auff vnd laz in dar y<g ref="#combuml"></g>n <abbr>v<ex>er</ex><am><g ref="#combcomma_er"></g></am>ge<g ref="#slong">s</g>en</abbr> <g ref="#tridotright"></g> ###<note>Am Ende der Zeile Text gelöscht.</note></seg><seg>
				<lb n="N012"></lb><g ref="#para"></g> Ettleich machent auch punt wey<g ref="#combuml"></g>n von roten <abbr>weinper<ex>e</ex><am><g ref="#bar_e"></g></am>n</abbr> . dy<g ref="#combuml"></g> <abbr>neme<ex>n</ex><am><g ref="#bar_n"></g></am>t</abbr> 
				<lb n="N013"></lb>gancze weinper . wol auff ein gut tret<g ref="#slong">s</g>chaff vol . mit ganczen
